description: The foodies of Kissimmee are certainly feeling the chemistry with the gourmet gastronomy found at the terrifically scientific Burger Lab truck. Having mastered the art & science of developing mouthwatering flavors, the geniuses behind Burger Lab are serving up an innovative selection of homemade sauces and condiments that all go beautifully with their hand-crafted burger creations, including...Smoke Burger- juicy Angus beef, fresh avocado, cilantro, caramelized red onion, crisp bacon, pepper jack cheese, and smoke sauceChicken Burger- perfectly seasoned ground chicken patty, fresh spinach, delightful mango chutneyVeggie Burger- savory black bean patty, spinach, tomato, avocadoThe conclusion? Absolutely delicious. For all this and much more, make your way to Burger Lab and experience the experiment that defies the laws of tastiness.
name: Burger Lab
